metatags.og:title: Violence flares at Trump rallies
metatags.og:description: Summer’s coming. And the rising temperatures, combined with Donald Trump’s extreme rhetoric and an uptick in violence outside his rallies have made conditions ripe for an unsettled season ahead. With the California primary just days away, and the GOP national convention looming in Cleveland, protesters have chased Trump supporters, blocked cars from leaving rallies and thrown eggs at backers of the presumptive Republican presidential nominee. POLITICO takes a look at some of the recent violence.
metatags.twitter:creator: @politico
